{"tid":56364,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"［新手］10k點先可以跑快啲？","createTime":"2016-12-27T07:41:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-15T06:53:57.000Z","uid":69091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c52f6dfdb05b08303e8957e9b522c277adea94f2","tid":56364,"uid":69091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T07:41:56.000Z","msg":"絲，第一次報渣馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n目標60-70分鐘內完成<br />\n暫時都係跑緊4/5k 6'03-6'35/k<br />\n應該點練？求高人指點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d39cf60311b801b78acb0cc3e1346b6090badbe","tid":56364,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T07:43:00.000Z","msg":"好耐冇跑，留名學野"},{"pid":"8f0aeb6b4e04b9c310da183d092bab2d31625e0d","tid":56364,"uid":2114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T07:43:58.000Z","msg":"6.35 min/km<br />\n10km應該65分鐘內就完到<br />\n最緊要做到均速"},{"pid":"830bd3fa8361801c8b2c50833448a68a4c9f5e85","tid":56364,"uid":5513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T07:49:20.000Z","msg":"去運動場 一星期跑一次令自己覺得好辛苦既4至5k <br />\n幾辛苦都都撐住  之後果幾日就慢跑 recover同練氣"},{"pid":"ef74cd1531cdfca23cfe55a0fbba49b574264f59","tid":56364,"uid":69091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T07:52:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>6.35 min/km<br />\n10km應該65分鐘內就完到<br />\n最緊要做到均速</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果進取啲想1粒鐘內完成可以點做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋我未試過一次跑6k以上 驚唔夠氣跑10k<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n應該點樣加長距離？"},{"pid":"1befc2fe806c74d6c8b0fc6be5674d3fee1e8a4c","tid":56364,"uid":52692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T07:54:06.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"966c5fe925a8d89aead8e6376129532f31288ec9","tid":56364,"uid":54740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T07:56:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>6.35 min/km<br />\n10km應該65分鐘內就完到<br />\n最緊要做到均速</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果進取啲想1粒鐘內完成可以點做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋我未試過一次跑6k以上 驚唔夠氣跑10k<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n應該點樣加長距離？</blockquote><br />\n去到現場你就唔知點解可以跑到好遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能係比身邊D人影響到<br />\n<br />\n小弟3年前跑10k馬 大約60-70mins<br />\n但明明練果陣跑3K都就死咁 最後唔知點解完成到<br />\n好啦..我都係交返比呢度既長跑巴媽說明一下"},{"pid":"3524eb07f4a25edf13ecba8c45fe31bbf18254f5","tid":56364,"uid":48442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T07:58:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4952e148f84566cf90ff0d75738d72b449c2e1db","tid":56364,"uid":40940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T08:07:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去運動場 一星期跑一次令自己覺得好辛苦既4至5k <br />\n幾辛苦都都撐住  之後果幾日就慢跑 recover同練氣</blockquote><br />\n而家運動係好科學化ga la.....<br />\n有晒數字可以跟"},{"pid":"788caf2a054684b7aad0e1069cbdfa1593f87b69","tid":56364,"uid":2114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T08:09:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>6.35 min/km<br />\n10km應該65分鐘內就完到<br />\n最緊要做到均速</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果進取啲想1粒鐘內完成可以點做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋我未試過一次跑6k以上 驚唔夠氣跑10k<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n應該點樣加長距離？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實跑10km最辛苦係頭嗰5-6km<br />\n之後嗰4km只要唔好忽然爆就無問題<br />\n<br />\n你問點樣1粒鐘內完到<br />\n我都答你唔到<br />\n因為我最快都係做到64分鐘，好廢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e9e7243b6fdc9de7971077533034fd0dcf68e4b","tid":56364,"uid":7075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T08:24:58.000Z","msg":"keep住唔好停 hold住個節奏 我暫時都跑50分"},{"pid":"bf6213314792a8dac1bdf671f20d062ce3411198","tid":56364,"uid":46548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T08:26:22.000Z","msg":"跑正式比賽前最好練過幾次10k<br />\n(慢慢加長練跑路線)<br />\n試下邊個均速係啱啱好到終點你跑唔到<br />\n<br />\n持之以恆咁練就會慢慢進步<br />\n不過唔好期望每次練都快之前好多(半分鐘)<br />\n因為如果你每次都跑盡既話<br />\n其實進步既都係十零秒<br />\n(仲要已經係好好好!)<br />\n所以希望你唔好咁著眼於個時間<br />\n<br />\n飲食方面要有足夠營養畀佢生肌肉<br />\n(可以食多啲有蛋白質既食物)<br />\n另外 就算唔練跑 每日都拉下筋"},{"pid":"24976d2eb9065010e6d7941409ebf919e0089748","tid":56364,"uid":32612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T08:27:41.000Z","msg":"跑過nb搞既10k<br />\n跑49分幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa7ad2247392388b94ebac9a7529dc2bfe5c2ba3","tid":56364,"uid":10204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T08:30:21.000Z","msg":"跑快d咪得"},{"pid":"b428b6f22630d0487e9af63748c949ea56716d7d","tid":56364,"uid":54079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T08:32:52.000Z","msg":"上年跑10k都係練過4，5次跑<br />\n如果練跑夠氣跑7k, 8k的話<br />\n到時跑10k應該ok的<br />\n因為最難頂係頭4,5 k<br />\n跑順左keep住就得"},{"pid":"562b0a3e6ed6233abb1872306bfb8299b6976170","tid":56364,"uid":6171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T08:44:39.000Z","msg":"有無去gym 操下腳？"},{"pid":"18931d24c31ae7e105c2c1102910db7f7c0daf33","tid":56364,"uid":69091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T09:55:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無去gym 操下腳？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇呀<br />\n唔識做機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去都淨係用跑步機/單車機"},{"pid":"facc7a0e89d633053ec94d26b4aee10f5f88908c","tid":56364,"uid":51105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T09:56:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>6.35 min/km<br />\n10km應該65分鐘內就完到<br />\n最緊要做到均速</blockquote><br />\n呢句話都幾撚廢"},{"pid":"d0f4161881d4ae574d2e2d1333c1b141f9c6c06c","tid":56364,"uid":69091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T09:59:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>跑正式比賽前最好練過幾次10k<br />\n(慢慢加長練跑路線)<br />\n試下邊個均速係啱啱好到終點你跑唔到<br />\n<br />\n持之以恆咁練就會慢慢進步<br />\n不過唔好期望每次練都快之前好多(半分鐘)<br />\n因為如果你每次都跑盡既話<br />\n其實進步既都係十零秒<br />\n(仲要已經係好好好!)<br />\n所以希望你唔好咁著眼於個時間<br />\n<br />\n飲食方面要有足夠營養畀佢生肌肉<br />\n(可以食多啲有蛋白質既食物)<br />\n另外 就算唔練跑 每日都拉下筋</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好詳盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Thanks！<br />\n依家跑緊4k 大概個令禮拜加多1k合唔合適<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4c97ad3460a36a6cd191e3f2434cc2d364c9e60","tid":56364,"uid":2114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T10:07:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>6.35 min/km<br />\n10km應該65分鐘內就完到<br />\n最緊要做到均速</blockquote><br />\n呢句話都幾撚廢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有啲人真係跑盡頭5km<br />\n之後就收檔<br />\n所以均速真係好重要<br />\n<br />\n利申：CE Maths B <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c23e01a27672c2bfcaad7a665588fc6887ba0428","tid":56364,"uid":30201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T10:09:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 留名學野<br />\n無幾耐前先傷咗膝頭哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08b4b438ddca19b146336257171aa1ea96f5f22f","tid":56364,"uid":6171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T10:14:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有無去gym 操下腳？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇呀<br />\n唔識做機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去都淨係用跑步機/單車機</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可以試下跟youtube 就咁bodyweight 做squat 同 lunge 做多d 下數"},{"pid":"f88d4e51de971a3a298b2bd9481df826f5f586e1","tid":56364,"uid":65579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T10:25:54.000Z","msg":"跑過渣馬跑10k 45mins倒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n平時我自己操跑就會分兩樣操。<br />\n耐力：跑海旁 走個10k練均速同頂乳酸。<br />\n速度：跑運動場 拎timer計時衝圈 。<br />\n<br />\n跑前一晚食多d碳水化合物（飯），早訓。<br />\n<br />\n利申：修PE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0891be6a89520671d8b1a5a9d352eb05befd4d95","tid":56364,"uid":69091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T10:28:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>6.35 min/km<br />\n10km應該65分鐘內就完到<br />\n最緊要做到均速</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果進取啲想1粒鐘內完成可以點做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋我未試過一次跑6k以上 驚唔夠氣跑10k<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n應該點樣加長距離？</blockquote><br />\n去到現場你就唔知點解可以跑到好遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能係比身邊D人影響到<br />\n<br />\n小弟3年前跑10k馬 大約60-70mins<br />\n但明明練果陣跑3K都就死咁 最後唔知點解完成到<br />\n好啦..我都係交返比呢度既長跑巴媽說明一下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n實戰我驚表現仲差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為跑運動場多 怕到時唔慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過好期待個種咁多人一齊跑既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2efd79899847966e1c37950e36c60502253794a3","tid":56364,"uid":48623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T10:32:18.000Z","msg":"變速練心肺機能"},{"pid":"f7e4893470e86eee38a47e05602aed86837a56e7","tid":56364,"uid":34154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T10:36:07.000Z","msg":"舊年練跑個陣10km至少要70分鐘，但係去到跑個日就63分鐘跑完 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"042aeb8a12af572f0ddfbbfcff518c0baba9fff7","tid":56364,"uid":60763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T10:40:03.000Z","msg":"練就跑里數先不求速度,均速完成<br />\n跑果日堅持跑,一步都唔好行 <br />\n60分鐘好快過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"788f64aeb81d035414c804b7b4fb2441f1ae88be","tid":56364,"uid":27164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T10:42:34.000Z","msg":"練個時要跑多過10k"},{"pid":"8a34693ad5f321aecf4c4fb30ff919885bf7cda4","tid":56364,"uid":69091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T10:48:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>舊年練跑個陣10km至少要70分鐘，但係去到跑個日就63分鐘跑完 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁犀利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跑完個下咪好爽好有成就感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a20abe2110416a79cec9859ca4d2ebc9e92b3a8","tid":56364,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T10:53:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>舊年練跑個陣10km至少要70分鐘，但係去到跑個日就63分鐘跑完 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁犀利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跑完個下咪好爽好有成就感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔奇，一黎前面多人擋風二黎有人一齊跑係會快d"},{"pid":"55a898e75b8749d35a944f4a095b7a91dc2bfeed","tid":56364,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T10:55:20.000Z","msg":"練好呼吸法先，通常快既都係口吸鼻呼，但基於香港環境唔建議<br />\n練個時都係路程優先過速度，跑得完自然會慢慢快<br />\n利伸，練跑最快52，渣馬訓得1個鐘結果號到嘔都係53分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d23a77b48e3ac9eb1f0921435bfa2658cbdd3adb","tid":56364,"uid":5519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T11:08:03.000Z","msg":"未試過跑10k<br />\n不過跑開5k 25.46跑完<br />\n我都係慢慢咁加上去同慢慢加速先而家咁"},{"pid":"116a38330fdaaf74082e1b6c8d5352e98726436d","tid":56364,"uid":40445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T11:17:49.000Z","msg":"慢慢練，冇速成方法<br />\n我跑咗年半，由2.5k跑到死死下，到而家跑到半馬<br />\n跑得舒服最重要，跑得快又冇獎嘅"},{"pid":"db490d6a5bb2c02e9dc9b262f0d916a22097e899","tid":56364,"uid":38299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T11:26:58.000Z","msg":"尻跑<br />\n利申 10k pb 35分，半馬 pb1.20"},{"pid":"0f18f1afdbb655370b9326651aa2794fced24c8c","tid":56364,"uid":34154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T11:38:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>舊年練跑個陣10km至少要70分鐘，但係去到跑個日就63分鐘跑完 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁犀利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跑完個下咪好爽好有成就感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔奇，一黎前面多人擋風二黎有人一齊跑係會快d</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都唔知點解個陣會無啦啦跑快左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b67ee3db2eb9d480adb9dfa36a761294c8fccd4a","tid":56364,"uid":68083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T11:43:44.000Z","msg":"試下彩雲跑去西貢(經壁屋）"},{"pid":"75c5142012d91dad18a31b646bf3f3923d39d670","tid":56364,"uid":5750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T11:44:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"33ce34c21df7323c659be23765de17fc7fb9fdfc","tid":56364,"uid":40623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T11:54:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>練好呼吸法先，通常快既都係口吸鼻呼，但基於香港環境唔建議<br />\n練個時都係路程優先過速度，跑得完自然會慢慢快<br />\n利伸，練跑最快52，渣馬訓得1個鐘結果號到嘔都係53分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 口吸唔係短跑先用架咩 我長跑係鼻吸口呼</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n口吸鼻呼緊係錯啦<br />\n試下冬天咁凍咁乾<br />\n口吸鼻呼跑一陣就係咁先"},{"pid":"2f16ab4ab899808a11c35fb7a1babaf20347fc0d","tid":56364,"uid":69091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T11:58:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>練好呼吸法先，通常快既都係口吸鼻呼，但基於香港環境唔建議<br />\n練個時都係路程優先過速度，跑得完自然會慢慢快<br />\n利伸，練跑最快52，渣馬訓得1個鐘結果號到嘔都係53分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 口吸唔係短跑先用架咩 我長跑係鼻吸口呼</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSame<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30c51206c56d100bbe85e5c399b096c7052d611d","tid":56364,"uid":67876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T12:52:19.000Z","msg":"真心睇恆心既<br />\n個人為例：<br />\n我一開始又肥又扁平足<br />\n開始個時公園下面二百米都冇既公園<br />\n跑一次都死死下<br />\n之後keep往大約跑一日休兩日<br />\n次次都盡量跑到自己身體想停就得<br />\n身體自自然然會愈跑愈耐<br />\n最緊要揾到自己節奏<br />\n跑個時最好唔好理時間 長度個喲<br />\nFor比賽就去多喲運動場跑<br />\n會有喲師兄教你<br />\n我就跑街多 興趣同減肥<br />\n利申：街跑多 10k 50分鐘內"},{"pid":"75fdfb1f56f7bda74f3d6fe01eacc0062df1fc52","tid":56364,"uid":9136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T13:46:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>變速練心肺機能</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我中學練長跑都係咁"},{"pid":"4af576fe0613b6a7bb1cabb34e43d1876da50d35","tid":56364,"uid":60256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T14:32:06.000Z","msg":"跑5次1500m（要出力跑）<br />\n每次休息3分鐘<br />\n<br />\n利：我自己鳩綀"},{"pid":"ac7143f6f98ebc7e1ded3113bd67799402f27947","tid":56364,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T14:52:36.000Z","msg":"10km 用跑100米速度跑晒全程可以破紀錄"},{"pid":"1015de4b617f1dd6ef4d7744f1b7d132de7855de","tid":56364,"uid":46548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T14:55:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>跑正式比賽前最好練過幾次10k<br />\n(慢慢加長練跑路線)<br />\n試下邊個均速係啱啱好到終點你跑唔到<br />\n<br />\n持之以恆咁練就會慢慢進步<br />\n不過唔好期望每次練都快之前好多(半分鐘)<br />\n因為如果你每次都跑盡既話<br />\n其實進步既都係十零秒<br />\n(仲要已經係好好好!)<br />\n所以希望你唔好咁著眼於個時間<br />\n<br />\n飲食方面要有足夠營養畀佢生肌肉<br />\n(可以食多啲有蛋白質既食物)<br />\n另外 就算唔練跑 每日都拉下筋</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好詳盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Thanks！<br />\n依家跑緊4k 大概個令禮拜加多1k合唔合適<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n差唔多啦<br />\n你二月四號跑其實得返四五個禮拜<br />\n按情況加里數 總之最後嗰星期係跑10k (約3次)<br />\n<br />\n同埋見到你話係運動場跑<br />\n其實唔係太好<br />\n因為逆時針跑向左轉彎會練到右腳大力啲 <br />\n長距離儘量跑返街"},{"pid":"31e9fedc98f32fb85774ba464e266ef3a092a9ea","tid":56364,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T14:56:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>練好呼吸法先，通常快既都係口吸鼻呼，但基於香港環境唔建議<br />\n練個時都係路程優先過速度，跑得完自然會慢慢快<br />\n利伸，練跑最快52，渣馬訓得1個鐘結果號到嘔都係53分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 口吸唔係短跑先用架咩 我長跑係鼻吸口呼</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSame<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我自己都鼻吸口呼，但係人地話口吸會快D，但我唔想試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8679aa62d2270d195a9be6d981ef6dcc990d7ba1","tid":56364,"uid":15745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T14:57:08.000Z","msg":"建議你10k 可以allin今晚利記"},{"pid":"3998e0a8018012e5b08a4a41fc6c475f4c91de78","tid":56364,"uid":69024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T15:58:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試下彩雲跑去西貢(經壁屋）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a359d64f35bfc47880606a2bfb460c6f45c9229f","tid":56364,"uid":69091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T16:57:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上年跑10k都係練過4，5次跑<br />\n如果練跑夠氣跑7k, 8k的話<br />\n到時跑10k應該ok的<br />\n因為最難頂係頭4,5 k<br />\n跑順左keep住就得</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n練4、5次就跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n應該平時有操開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"761bc8a160ccfc91cbad3376a0b59cc8f5a0e518","tid":56364,"uid":69091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T17:03:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>跑正式比賽前最好練過幾次10k<br />\n(慢慢加長練跑路線)<br />\n試下邊個均速係啱啱好到終點你跑唔到<br />\n<br />\n持之以恆咁練就會慢慢進步<br />\n不過唔好期望每次練都快之前好多(半分鐘)<br />\n因為如果你每次都跑盡既話<br />\n其實進步既都係十零秒<br />\n(仲要已經係好好好!)<br />\n所以希望你唔好咁著眼於個時間<br />\n<br />\n飲食方面要有足夠營養畀佢生肌肉<br />\n(可以食多啲有蛋白質既食物)<br />\n另外 就算唔練跑 每日都拉下筋</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好詳盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Thanks！<br />\n依家跑緊4k 大概個令禮拜加多1k合唔合適<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n差唔多啦<br />\n你二月四號跑其實得返四五個禮拜<br />\n按情況加里數 總之最後嗰星期係跑10k (約3次)<br />\n<br />\n同埋見到你話係運動場跑<br />\n其實唔係太好<br />\n因為逆時針跑向左轉彎會練到右腳大力啲 <br />\n長距離儘量跑返街</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又真係無諗過哩個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n等我揾下近近地路線跑街先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n浄係跑過大埔海濱一次定兩次"},{"pid":"326c0c4e3ae6bd0f67cd54f62b068d50e0b0eac3","tid":56364,"uid":69091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T17:17:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試下彩雲跑去西貢(經壁屋）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我又真係住附近<br />\n上網睇過下 跟92號巴士跑？"}]}